{"id": 1169, "genre": 1001, "title": "你对各种着装规范有什么困扰or不满？", "description": "Dress Code什么的，规定太细就头疼。", "record_count": 2086, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160813101435okLzpPQe6ZuRMvC4.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-16T03:00:08Z", "options": [{"id": 108032, "content": "校服明明只有春秋款～却要一年四季都要穿！", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693305}, {"id": 108034, "content": "冬天只能穿冬季校服夏天只能穿夏季校服，这是在冻死和热死间切换", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717322}, {"id": 108035, "content": "学校规定女生冬天也要穿裙子和裤袜 不管多冷 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 252969}, {"id": 108292, "content": "中国的校服要传统刚强讲究的是德贤，朴素。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719494}, {"id": 108038, "content": "格子衬衫是你们的工服吗？（我真不是针对ITer）", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238743}, {"id": 108039, "content": "作为一名健身教练要求上班时间穿白鞋!!现在的白鞋有多贵知道吗?!而且大部分都是网眼的材质有多容易落土和多不容易刷知道吗?!", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 120240}, {"id": 108040, "content": "校服总是跟大件   学生总是要用钱去改", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717391}, {"id": 108041, "content": "感觉很赞", "image": "img/option/option/20160816132043sx6WLEpc5bQCHFSl.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670696}, {"id": 108042, "content": "测试看看", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670696}, {"id": 108043, "content": "为什么有人总以为女生要穿裙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631732}, {"id": 108044, "content": "房产中介衬衫白，交易黑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149680}, {"id": 108045, "content": "作为广告?，没有着装限制?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628098}, {"id": 108046, "content": "白衬衫加黑西裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717319}, {"id": 108047, "content": "男人为什么不给穿裙子", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 108048, "content": "没有着装要求不代表可以不洗澡！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 272586}, {"id": 108049, "content": "不知道是不是因为深圳的校服好看的原因，冬天羽绒服必须穿在外套里面，球长啥样我长啥样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717469}, {"id": 108052, "content": "我们高中秋冬校服是牛角扣灯芯绒大衣，大学是订制衬衫领带制服，必须穿无装饰的黑高跟皮鞋，裙摆必须熨平…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666658}, {"id": 108053, "content": "Smart Casual真的很难拿捏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245557}, {"id": 108054, "content": "我不明白30度以上的天气还要求衬衫长裤皮鞋，国内公司老板是否明白不是所有上班族上下班都有空调无缝衔接的！你们TMD的35度40度的天穿衬衫西裤打领带坐地铁公交上下班试试！", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 204422}, {"id": 108055, "content": "当初就看中了想穿啥就穿啥才选了做广告创意人", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 108312, "content": "上班穿拖鞋，下班穿运动鞋，额(⊙o⊙)…我是厨师。。。", "image": "img/option/option/20160817175027IPhtX80Gkegl7L4S", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719636}, {"id": 108057, "content": "没有系统介绍什么年龄穿什么合适…衣服什么样都有…而且不会搭配", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}, {"id": 108059, "content": "统一着装太过呆板单调", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711123}, {"id": 108060, "content": "高跟鞋根本就是限制女性效率。请问你雇我是为了上班还是为了看？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693547}, {"id": 108061, "content": "上身衬衫下身运动裤…怎么穿怎么别扭", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287118}, {"id": 108062, "content": "读书的时候，下雨天还不许穿拖鞋和凉鞋。我不懂老师和学校领导们怎么想的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651447}, {"id": 108063, "content": "好看也就算了，关键是衣服丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 706684}, {"id": 108064, "content": "中小学生的学生服面料太次了，味大质差。本来就是学生自己出钱，为什么不从环保考虑一下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707206}, {"id": 108065, "content": "所有女性制服不够性感", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 706122}, {"id": 108067, "content": "学校规定天天穿校服", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563467}, {"id": 108070, "content": "我们初中校服跟水泥厂工服样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715212}, {"id": 108071, "content": "一穿正式的工作服，就不是自己了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493118}, {"id": 108072, "content": "作为一个在办公室穿拖鞋还时不时盘腿的吃瓜群众，对吐槽的各位深表同情", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682496}, {"id": 108073, "content": "打扮得热情一点就被说成了骚(눈_눈)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717624}, {"id": 108074, "content": "高中校服是中山装（热血高校那样婶儿的）校内校外怎么穿都不管 但进出时候校门必须把扣子全扣上", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711059}, {"id": 108075, "content": "夏天太热了难过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717630}, {"id": 108076, "content": "不能穿牛仔裤上班呵呵辞职了", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162244}, {"id": 108077, "content": "不能涂指甲油", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179812}, {"id": 108078, "content": "大学刚毕业就在Wall St工作，做最基本的associate，上班第一天；老板过来直接问我：需要我放你一天假学习dress code吗？如果不，去HR那里寻求帮助！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 70594}, {"id": 108079, "content": "初中有男生头发不许超过耳朵，女生不许留刘海的规定", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 423267}, {"id": 108081, "content": "为啥初中校服要是绿色的？爱护眼睛也不能这样啊……怪丑的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668539}, {"id": 108082, "content": "不能穿无袖，不能穿超短裙，不能牛仔裤，衣，最好穿的像卖保险似的", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685442}, {"id": 109618, "content": "我喜西装男", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724682}, {"id": 109619, "content": "中意西装男", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724682}, {"id": 108084, "content": "想起了初中的麻布口袋校服⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 108085, "content": "卡扣", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670696}, {"id": 108089, "content": "想學習怎麼優雅的穿確無從下手", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529032}, {"id": 108090, "content": "减肥减肥减肥呢你放假放假放假就春节放假放假就放假放假放假参加春节放假放假放假放假放假放假放假春节放假超级超级超级风景就充分接触肌肤可看到激发你的减肥减肥课就放假放假参加春节放假妇女节机场飞机飞将军", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670696}, {"id": 108095, "content": "穿正装上班的工作太难受了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 717761}, {"id": 108096, "content": "第一个想起保险套装", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686424}]}